  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In the <em>xy</em>-plane, line <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math> has a slope of <math alttext=\"5\"><mn>5</mn>\n</math> and a <em>y</em>-intercept of <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 0 comma negative 35 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>35</mn></mrow></mrow></mfenced></math>. What is the <em>x</em>-coordinate of the <em>x</em>-intercept of line <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": null,
